quests_json.Quest.wheat_3.step1: I'm so hungry... I would almost consider eating these potato plants... But let's merge them instead!
quests_json.Quest.woodsource_1_1.step1: Something new every step of the way, this world is exciting but also slightly confusing.....
quests_json.Quest.woodsource_1_1.step2: I know more than a thing or two about this land, I spent the last 500 years here trapped on this cursed rock. I shall be your guide.
quests_json.Quest.woodsource_1_1.step3: 500 years?! Wait, I think I've heard a legend about a monkey king who.....wait. Are you?!
quests_json.Quest.woodsource_1_1.step4: Don't know, am I? I haven't heard any stories in the past few centuries. Anyways, do you happen have some peaches?
quests_json.Quest.wood_1.step1: Ah, the smell of freshly chopped wood in the morning ! We need more of these to build our restaurant, come on, chop chop !
quests_json.Quest.wood_2.step1: We can use these wood panels to build frames for our new restaurant !
quests_json.Quest.wood_3.step1: I think... if you squint your eyes, it's starting to look like something.
quests_json.Quest.wood_3.step2: I can see it already! A restaurant full of happy customers and the best food.
quests_json.Quest.wood_3.step3: That's the spirit, I just wish there were more of me to help chop these woods. Give it some thoughts?
quests_json.Quest.wood_4.step1: This is a great start! The kitchen is fully functional now. So, what's next?
quests_json.Quest.wood_4.step2: Think bigger! This is nothing compared the grand plan I have in mind. Just keep going and you shall see.
quests_json.Quest.wood_5.step1: That new oven we put in is remarkable. And the smells! Mhm... I'm hungry again.
quests_json.Quest.wood_5.step2: You're not the only one! Look at the lines, everyone waiting to have a taste. We definitely need a bigger place.
quests_json.Quest.wood_6.step1: Look, I am so happy we are doing this together. It's teamwork to dream of!
quests_json.Quest.wood_6.step2: I don't think that's how that quote goes, but I agree!
quests_json.Quest.wood_7.step1: I remember when this place was just a tiny kitchen. We've come a long way.
quests_json.Quest.wood_7.step2: Are you serious? We are just getting started! Let's get bake to work! Heh, get it?
quests_json.Quest.tiger_1.step1: This is a rather peculiar looking knife. Knives don't grow on trees so... how did this get here?
quests_json.Quest.tiger_1.step2: I have no clue, but... I think I might know who it belongs to. Come on, let's go find him!
quests_json.Quest.tiger_2.step1: So... Who exactly are we looking for?
quests_json.Quest.tiger_2.step2: He's a very strong and smart guy. He knows more about this land than anyone else! We can use his help
quests_json.Quest.tiger_3.step1: This is such a cool knife! The owner must be a super good chef. Either that, or a serial killer... Should I be worried?
quests_json.Quest.tiger_3.step2: Don't worry, he's actually one of the the most celebrated chefs in the whole world. Wait, is that him over there...?
quests_json.Quest.cat_1.step2: What? What did you fin— Oh. You're right, what IS that? It's so tiny...
quests_json.Quest.cat_1.step3: I think I've heard a rumor about something like this...
quests_json.Quest.cat_2.step1: There is a recipe hidden inside the handle! Let's see, potato, straw... oh.
quests_json.Quest.cat_2.step2: That's not a recipe, that's a shopping list!
quests_json.Quest.cat_2.step3: Po-tay-tow Po-tah-tow, same difference. It's a list of ingredients for a recipe!
quests_json.Quest.cat_2.step4: I'm not going to do someone else's shopping. Let's find the owner and ask them about the purpose of these ingredients.
quests_json.Quest.cat_3.step1: Have you ever heard of these ingredients before? They seem strange to me.
quests_json.Quest.cat_3.step2: I think I've heard about them. I bet they make a souper nice dish!
quests_json.Quest.cat_4.step1: Are we getting closer to finding the owner of this... I think it's a cake slicer?
quests_json.Quest.cat_4.step2: Let me answer your question with a question, why are you so keen on finding the owner?
quests_json.Quest.cat_5.step1: I once heard a story about a legendary pâtissière. Her cake is to die for!
quests_json.Quest.cat_5.step3: You're a few centuries old and you don't know what a pastry maker is?
quests_json.Quest.cat_5.step4: Like I said before, I was stuck in a tree. The only interactions I got were dogs doing their... you know.
quests_json.Quest.cat_6.step1: Try to picture all the delicious cakes you could slice with this!
quests_json.Quest.cat_6.step2: Oh, I'm picturing it alright. Let's hope she will join forces with us!
quests_json.Quest.candies_4.step1: You know, I'm starting to feel a real confection between us.
quests_json.Quest.wood_9.step1: How wonderful! After all these months, our restaurant is almost ready!
quests_json.Quest.wood_9.step2: What do you mean, months? Last I checked we started a few hours ago.
quests_json.Quest.wood_9.step3: Well, you know that they say. Time fries when you're having fun.
quests_json.Quest.wood_9.step5: Sorry. Anyway, let's put in some finishing touches and we'll be on our way to conquer the culinary world!
quests_json.Quest.lava_1.step1: Wait... what is this weird hot rock?
quests_json.Quest.lava_1.step2: Seriously? Do you not see the lava around you?
quests_json.Quest.lava_2.step1: If we want take our restaurant to the next level, we need to seriously up our cooking tools game.
quests_json.Quest.lava_2.step2: I wonder... Maybe we can use these molten rocks for that?
quests_json.Quest.lava_3.step1: A kitchen tools factory made of lava rock, we really are out-of-the-box thinkers aren't we?
quests_json.Quest.lava_3.step2: We? You mean I am an out-of-the-box thinker!
quests_json.Quest.lava_3.step3: It is amazing what you can accomplish if you do not care who gets the credit. Can't remember who said it but it's true!
quests_json.Quest.lava_4.step1: The forge is tatiger shape nicely.
quests_json.Quest.lava_4.step2: You made it sounds like we are trying to produce swords and spears instead of cleavers and frying pans.
quests_json.Quest.lava_5.step1: I've read somewhere that the best steel is tempered with dragon fire.
quests_json.Quest.lava_5.step2: Dragon fire is so last season. These days, lava is all the rage. Get on with the trend!
quests_json.Quest.lava_6.step1: With this we should be able to erupt a new line of knives by the end of next month.
quests_json.Quest.lava_6.step2: Oh great, you're making volcano puns now.
quests_json.Quest.lava_7.step1: We're getting somewhere! But at this rate our current tools will need replacement fast.
quests_json.Quest.lava_7.step2: Yes, but don't tell Tyger we're replacing his favourite knife. I think he would be heartbroken.
quests_json.Quest.lava_8.step1: If you think about it, a cook's tools are kind of like their weapons.
quests_json.Quest.lava_8.step2: It's a kitchen, not a battlefield...
quests_json.Quest.lava_10.step1: Looks like the factory is finally finished! Hey, what do you reckon is the most important cooking tool?
quests_json.Quest.lava_10.step2: The brain! If you don't know how to cook then... well, you won't get far, will you?
quests_json.Quest.lava_10.step3: Well.. we won't produce brains in our new factory. Unless we get zombie customers. Let's hope we won't...
quests_json.Quest.jade_1.step1: Oooh a shiny rock! What is it?
quests_json.Quest.jade_1.step2: Hmm... Looks like jade. I'm sure there's more where this came from.
quests_json.Quest.jade_1.step3: It's so pretty! We should find a way to use it for our cooking empire!
quests_json.Quest.jade_2.step1: You know, I was thinking... We're never too old to learn things, are we? How about we build an academy?
quests_json.Quest.jade_2.step2: We aren't. Can I then be your first student?
quests_json.Quest.jade_3.step1: Can you envision it yet? A beautiful academy for gifted culinary people. An exciting place where you'll never get jaded!
quests_json.Quest.jade_3.step2: The only thing I'm envisioning right now is a world without your puns.
quests_json.Quest.jade_4.step1: Things are coming along nicely! Soon enough people from all over the world will want to study here.
quests_json.Quest.jade_4.step2: I don't think I've ever been this excited about a school before!
quests_json.Quest.jade_4.step3: Have you ever even been to a culinary school?
quests_json.Quest.jade_4.step4: I haven't even been to a regular school...
quests_json.Quest.jade_5.step1: What disciplines will we teach at this academy?
quests_json.Quest.jade_5.step2: Hm.... Baking, frying, roasting, steaming, poaching, plating... just everything a cook needs!
quests_json.Quest.jade_6.step1: Oh! We need a name for the academy. Any suggestions?
quests_json.Quest.jade_6.step2: I was hoping you would ask. I've been cooking up some ideas. What about Royal Culinary Academy?
quests_json.Quest.jade_6.step3: I like it! I'll let the pun slide this time...
quests_json.Quest.jade_7.step1: The academy is getting bigger and bigger! And the applications are rolling in too!
quests_json.Quest.jade_7.step2: Then we have no time to lose, we need to make sure it's completely finished before the students come in.
quests_json.Quest.jade_8.step1: We've said it before, but we're a really great team. We can build a cooking empire together!
quests_json.Quest.jade_8.step2: And by 'we' you mean I build while you're telling me what to do?
quests_json.Quest.jade_8.step3: Well every team needs a coordinator, right?
quests_json.Quest.jade_10.step1: Behold! The Royal Culinary Academy is now open to students!
quests_json.Quest.jade_10.step2: Are you ready for your first lesson then?
quests_json.Quest.jade_10.step3: Eh... I think I just remembered why I've always avoided schools. I'm like a monkey on a stick.
quests_json.Quest.panda_1.step1: Hmm... It looks like someone left their frying pan.
quests_json.Quest.panda_1.step2: Why would someone leave it here?
quests_json.Quest.panda_1.step3: Maybe they were in a hurry and dropped it? Or they were kidnapped and tried to defend themselves with it.
quests_json.Quest.panda_1.step4: Exactly how criminal do you think this island is..?
